      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six engine and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Engineered for performance, it maintains excellent mechanical health with the critical double-VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced for long-term chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential ensures superior traction out of apexes, while the suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers to sharpen turn-in response. Though the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear power all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. Shod in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this M3 is dialed in for the enthusiast who values tactile feedback and mechanical purity.",
